                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18111030-89-off490 t18111030-89-cd491"></join>, a bridle, value 8 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18111030-89-victim759" type="victimName">
                  John 
                  Boswell
               <interp inst="t18111030-89-victim759" type="surname" value="Boswell"></interp>
